{"tid":1818103,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[有相]文尼開槍殺死同鄉！","createTime":"2020-01-09T15:19:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-09T21:16:59.000Z","uid":2429,"like":3,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e3e086d8c32ecc4da88d6c101fb4100ff63bb8f5","tid":1818103,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T15:19:10.000Z","msg":"【殘忍人類】偷獵者射殺大猩猩 將屍體當作戰利品一同合照<br />\n2020-01-08<br />\n即時國際<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200107/large/1578386107_c758.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200107%2Flarge%2F1578386107_c758.jpg&h=bde2bbc7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n捕獵者射殺大猩猩後與牠合照(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n保護大猩猩組織「L'Association Gorilla」在網上發佈了照片，激起了關注動物權利人士的憤怒。照片中可見一群相信是非法捕獵者的男子，圍着一隻大猩猩拍照，而照片中的大猩猩可能在拍照前已被捕獵者射殺。<br />\n<br />\n該組織指，照片的拍攝地點應該剛果共和國首都布拉柴維爾（Brazzaville）附近，大猩猩是被「非法射殺死亡」，「一隻漂亮樸素的大猩猩被非法射殺後，再被獵人展示的震撼照片，只是數日前在剛果西部布拉柴維爾拍攝」，組織強調剛果法律嚴厲禁止殺害受保護動物。<br />\n<br />\n照片中見到一群男子將獵槍圍在大猩猩身邊，然後圍着牠拍照，而該大猩猩相信已被他們殺害，該組織稱，「這是我們不想再見到&hellip;&hellip;」。<br />\n<br />\n世界自然基金會（WWF）資料顯示，野生大猩猩正受到偷獵者、疾病和森林砍伐的威脅，目前野外山地大猩猩數量僅逾1,000隻。慈善機構「Ape Alliance」表示，由於缺乏有效的司法系統監管，非法捕獵大猩猩活動一直無法遏止。<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日郵報》<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20200108/60459124\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200108%2F60459124&d=eKFc4b3FQa1ReKUUeYtKdCL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=dabeb246\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200108%2F60459124&h=df8bdab2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20200108/60459124</a><br />\n<br />\n力架笑甚麽，你也是猩猩。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37bf20a4f135e60dcbfc63834df426aa90f235e0","tid":1818103,"uid":34858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T15:39:57.000Z","msg":"剛果唔關事吧"},{"pid":"efe03c92f436aaf2e91f3a470112fcb982d5ed31","tid":1818103,"uid":62891,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T15:56:54.000Z","msg":"好撚好笑呀你"},{"pid":"a003fde63dcd9f3a526f7b52d17c4ce022922cc7","tid":1818103,"uid":280329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T16:01:42.000Z","msg":"呢D第三世界國家 邊有得救...<br />\n香港而家都步向咁既邊緣"},{"pid":"c8b9d748fdef229c4aa3b5469ec00622709bdce3","tid":1818103,"uid":61002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T21:16:59.000Z","msg":"哇  wwi嘅槍嚟?"}]}